[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Illuminate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 4 ====
HEADWORD: Illuminate
<hw>Il*lu"mi*nate</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is enlightened; esp.,
a pretender to extraordinary light and knowledge.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>illuminated</ent>⟦br⟧
